            "criteria": {
                "textblock": "Inclusion Criteria:\n\n          -  Critical/Intensive care or Neurocritical care admission\n\n          -  Admission for/with acute encephalopathy defined as a rapidly developing (over less\n             than 4 weeks, but usually within hours to a few days) pathobiological process in the\n             brain; including delirium or subsyndromal (DSM V definition) or coma (Glasgow coma\n             scale score < 9)\n\n          -  SARS-COV-2 infection (respiratory or other PCR specimen)\n\n          -  Age \u2265 18 years\n\n        Exclusion Criteria:\n\n        - Opposition to study participation from the patient itself or patient surrogate"
            },
